The paper deals with interference management in a wireless network, which involves topics such as information theory (cs.IT), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), systems and control (cs.SY), multimedia (cs.MM), and computer communication (cs.COM). However, since the paper focuses on the use of a reverse TDD protocol and wireless backhaul in a HetNet, which are more related to information theory and networking, respectively, we can assume that cs.IT and cs.NI are the most likely categories.
